cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DC

This paper is about improving the accuracy of deep neural networks by going deeper and wider in their architectures, while overcoming the limitation of GPU DRAM. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses memory optimization techniques and performance issues, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
